
  Welcome to mycloverOS -- The OS that powers CloverStack
  --------------------------------------------------------

  Quick commands:
    cloverstack-ctl status     Show module status
    cloverstack-ctl list       List available modules
    cloverstack-ctl enable X   Enable a module
    myclover-update            Update system + modules

  Dashboard:  https://localhost:9443 (Portainer)
  Docs:       https://myclover.tech/docs

